title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 27 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 27 2022
description:
Senator Rick Scott talks to Clay and Buck about the situation in Ukraine, Biden's student loan forgiveness plan, the lawlessness at the southern border, the Disney controversy, and the conservative migration to the great state of Florida. New York's highest court strikes down Democrat redistricting. This is 100% true: Marjorie Taylor Greene quizzed in court on Independence Day movie. Pennsylvania Senate Candidate David McCormick joins C&B to make his case in the GOP primary. Tyrant King Smurf Fauci pronounces the pandemic over.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
